lin, Poor Richard's Almanack, 1763  >--------------------------------------------------------  >Gregory J. Rosmaita <unagi69@concentric.net>  >    WebMaster and Minister of Propaganda, VICUG NYC  >         <http://www.hicom.net/~oedipus/vicug/index.html>  >--------------------------------------------------------        

